ğ‘ğ¶ğ‘œğ‘‡ï¼šnumber of CoT createdï¼Œthe CoT has to be used for at least one dealï¼› 

ğ‘ğ‘ƒğ‘Ÿğ¶ï¼šnumber of deals cleared under PrC contractsï¼› 

